開始作圖

全台家教薪資比較

choroLayer(spdf = TWN, df = TWN@data, var = "mean_salary", legend.title.txt = "average tutor's salary\nfor each county",legend.pos = "right")
cols <- carto.pal(pal1 = "green.pal", n1 = 2, pal2 = "red.pal", n2 = 4)
choroLayer(spdf = TWN, df = TWN@data, var = "mean_salary", 
           border = "grey40", lwd = 0.5,  
           legend.title.txt = "average tutor's salary\nfor each county", 
           legend.pos = "right",
           legend.values.rnd = 2, add = TRUE)
plot(TWN, border = "grey20", lwd = 0.75, add = TRUE)

全台家教薪資與各縣市所得比較

allsalary<- read_csv("各縣市所得_new.csv", col_names ="allsalary")
## Parsed with column specification:
## cols(
##   allsalary = col_integer()
## )
TWN@data<-cbind(TWN@data,allsalary)

choroLayer(spdf = TWN, df = TWN@data, var = "allsalary",legend.pos = "none")
cols <- carto.pal(pal1 = "green.pal", n1 = 2, pal2 = "red.pal", n2 = 4)
choroLayer(spdf = TWN, df = TWN@data, var = "allsalary", 
           col = cols, 
           border = "grey40", lwd = 0.5,  
           legend.title.txt = "average salary\nfor each county", 
           legend.values.rnd = 2, add = TRUE)
plot(TWN, border = "grey20", lwd = 0.75, add = TRUE)
propSymbolsLayer(spdf = TWN, df = TWN@data, 
                 var = "mean_salary",inches =0.5 , symbols = "bar", col = "yellow",
                 legend.pos = "right", legend.title.txt = "average tutor's salary\nfor each county", 
                 legend.style = "c")
